Document: Light2D
Path: godot/classes/class_light2d.rst
Summary: Defines a 2D light source that affects other 2D nodes.

Light2D

Inherits: Node2D < CanvasItem < Node < Object

A 2D light source. Affects all child CanvasItem nodes within its range.

Properties:

color (Color): The light's color.
energy (float): The light's energy (brightness). Default: 1.0.
offset (Vector2): The light's offset from its origin.
radius (float): The light's radius. Default: 0.0.
scale (Vector2): The light's scale. Default: (1, 1).
texture (Texture2D): The light's texture.
texture_filter (int): The texture filtering mode. Default: 0.
texture_repeat (int): The texture repeat mode. Default: 0.
visible_in_all_rooms (bool): If true, the light will be visible in all rooms. Default: false.
Shadow:

shadow_buffer_size (int): The size of the shadow buffer. Default: 1024.
shadow_color (Color): The shadow's color.
shadow_cpu_cast_bias (float): The bias for CPU shadow casting. Default: 0.0.
shadow_enable (bool): Enable shadows. Default: false.
shadow_filter (int): The shadow filter mode. Default: 0.
shadow_filter_smooth (float): The smoothness of the shadow filter. Default: 0.0.
shadow_gradient_length (float): The length of the shadow gradient. Default: 0.0.
shadow_item_cull_mask (int): The cull mask for shadow items. Default: 1.
shadow_item_shadow_color (Color): The shadow color for items.
shadow_item_shadow_mode (int): The shadow mode for items. Default: 0.
shadow_mode (int): The shadow mode. Default: 0.
shadow_normal_bias (float): The bias for shadow normals. Default: 0.0.
shadow_only (bool): If true, the light will only cast shadows. Default: false.
shadow_reverse_cull_face (bool): If true, the shadow will be reversed. Default: false.
shadow_texture_bias (float): The bias for shadow textures. Default: 0.0.
shadow_texture_offset (Vector2): The offset for shadow textures. Default: (0, 0).
shadow_texture_scale (Vector2): The scale for shadow textures. Default: (1, 1).
shadow_texture_rotation (float): The rotation for shadow textures. Default: 0.0.
shadow_transparent (bool): If true, the shadow will be transparent. Default: false.
shadow_wait_for_gpu_sync (bool): If true, the light will wait for GPU synchronization. Default: true.
Blend Mode:

blend_mode (int): The blend mode for the light. Default: 0.

