Path: godot/classes/class_light2d.rst
Summary: Describes the Light2D node, which casts light in a 2D environment with configurable color, energy, mode, range, and shadow properties.

Light2D
Casts light in a 2D environment. A light is defined as a color, an energy value, a mode (see constants), and various other parameters (range and shadows-related).
